init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see yourself as a baby, and then you watch your life unfold, moment by moment, as you age.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see your life as a child, as a teenager, as a young adult, and so on.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see your relationships, your successes, your failures, and your death.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You watch your life until the end, and then you are asked if you would like to be reincarnated.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are told that you get to choose.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You think about it for a while, and then you decide that you would like to be reincarnated as a rich, famous, and powerful person.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You will be able to help people, to make a real difference in the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You hope that you will still be able to feel the pain of others, and you wonder if you will be able to help people who are less fortunate

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They tell you that you are able to change your mind, but that you will lose all of your memories of your previous life if you do.
